BALTIMORE (AP) _ The winning numbers in Thursday evening’s drawing of the Maryland Lottery’s “Bonus Match 5” game were:
05-12-19-22-34, Bonus: 36
(five, twelve, nineteen, twenty-two, thirty-four; Bonus: thirty-six)
